    {<br>
    perform anti-AE kite code<br>
    }<br>
<br>
Simple fix. If you can get exp from it, you cant kite it, until it reaches its last 10% health, and is ready to run. You can still use them on stationary targets as you can now. Eliminates AE kiting, and still lets you farm greenies.<br>
